body: I can solve this issue, if you setup Jenkins CI here with Windows agent, so I can test my changes.

## solution 4

MySQLclient merges few static libraries into single one with https://github.com/mysql/mysql-server/blob/5.7/cmake/libutils.cmake. And it is portable solution. I did not try this one, I can't highlight problems.

We define our own cmake `ed25519_add_library`, which creates static library and enables `-fPIC`. Then, we merge static libraries into single shared `libed25519.so`. For all targets we define `EXCLUDE_FROM_ALL=ON` if `TESTING=ON`. 

This may satisfy requirements of both clients.
Please  describe this issue more. I don't see any code that changes compiler.
